{"tid":1868313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 澄清運送到機場的口罩是供前線人員使用　非運往外地","createTime":"2020-02-07T13:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T16:45:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ab802c663369dc89a1d1dc2b517bbee181f80a","tid":1868313,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"有網上圖片見到，有市民在機場入境大堂拍攝到有人運送懲教署製造的口罩，質疑政府將口罩運往外地。政府晚上透過社交平台「添馬台」澄清，指有關口罩是運送到機場供前線人員使用，呼籲公眾不要再故亂散播失實消息，強調自疫情開始，懲教署生產的口罩，再沒有供應給政府以外的機構，都是提供給政府各部門，特別是前線的衛生署及其他部門人員使用。"},{"pid":"cc079742476f1922deafb0e2cf41f718a34ba88b","tid":1868313,"uid":159870,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"圖？？？"},{"pid":"a446b1dcde4fdc0d4ba79425d56179fcfd8721c5","tid":1868313,"uid":108347,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:35:56.000Z","msg":"點解到今日都仲係冇SOURCE開PO,你都COPY得段野點解唔COPY埋個網址"},{"pid":"7cbf6eeb8616ca32fe42e3fec0b27df3241804d0","tid":1868313,"uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cc079742476f1922deafb0e2cf41f718a34ba88b","tid":1868313,"uid":159870,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"圖？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/84462288_140285367460464_8645095870594809856_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ohc=PyRd_hXeJpQAX-aA9Pw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=e416bb7b42dfc95091825683038b2c3d&amp;oe=5ED6C207\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F84462288_140285367460464_8645095870594809856_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ohc%3DPyRd_hXeJpQAX-aA9Pw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3De416bb7b42dfc95091825683038b2c3d%26oe%3D5ED6C207&h=496363fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76955ad92ab2c9cf6bee4af4a6eeea5892f2df0d","tid":1868313,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote